search_term: Find the official pricing page URL for Teamup Calendar (teamup-calendar.com). Only provide the exact URL to the pricing page, not a summary of pricing information.
response_text: The official pricing page for Teamup Calendar is: [https://www.teamup.com/pricing/](https://www.teamup.com/pricing/) .

Redistribution

The pricing plans above apply if you are using Teamup Calendars to support the operation of your own organization, internally or publicly, including embedding them into Web sites or as Facebook apps, and sharing calendar links with partners and clients. If you are integrating Teamup Calendar into a software product or service that is made available to third parties for free or for a fee, then you need a redistribution agreement with us. Please contact us for details.
